### 🔬 Key Mathematical Discoveries

#### 1. Mandelbrot & Fractal Deconstruction
```
Coastline Paradox: L(ε) = L₀ × ε^(1-D)
Fractal Dimension: D = lim[log N(ε) / log(1/ε)]
Granularity Correction: Δ_{g_i→g_j}(φ) = Σ Cov × β(g_k)
```

#### 2. Origin-Centric Fluid Dynamics
```
Relative Position: r_Q^(P)(t) = x_Q(t) - x_P(t)
Rate Function: R(x,t) = lim[N(x,Δt)/Δt]
Particle Frame Navier-Stokes: ∂v^(P)/∂t + (v^(P)·∇)v^(P) = -∇p^(P)/ρ + ν∇²v^(P) - a_P(t)
```

#### 3. AI Spreadsheet Architecture
```
Cell Type: Cell = ⟨Content, Type, State, Dependencies, Observers⟩
Deadband Trigger: Update if |v(t)-v(t-1)| > δ × max(|v(t)|,|v(t-1)|)
Agent Priority: Priority = α·Deadline + β·DependencyDepth + γ·ChangeMagnitude
```

#### 4. Constraint Theory & Stochastic Logic
```
Constraint Metric: κ(S) = 1 - log(N(S))/log(N₀)
Cognitive Fractal Dimension: D_c(S) = lim[log C(ε) / log(1/ε)]
Inference Sufficiency: Compute if (Cost_Accurate < Cost_Error × Prob_Error)
```

